). Small; mean and maximum 
<collectionCode box="[389,419,2001,2022]" country="France" name="Musee des Dinosaures d'Esperaza (Aude)" pageId="25" pageNumber="158">CS</collectionCode>
2015 and 
<quantity box="[536,631,2001,2022]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.173" pageId="25" pageNumber="158" unit="mm" value="2173.0">2173 µm</quantity>
. Scape short and thickset, 
<collectionCode box="[973,1002,177,198]" country="Sierra Leone" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:14608" name="University of Sierra Leone, Njala University College" pageId="25" pageNumber="158" type="Herbarium">SL</collectionCode>
/ 
<collectionCode box="[1030,1060,177,198]" country="France" name="Musee des Dinosaures d'Esperaza (Aude)" pageId="25" pageNumber="158">CS</collectionCode>
0.810, 
<collectionCode box="[1146,1175,177,198]" country="Sierra Leone" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:14608" name="University of Sierra Leone, Njala University College" pageId="25" pageNumber="158" type="Herbarium">SL</collectionCode>
/ Smax 8.32. Setae on eyes rather short, EyeHL 
<quantity box="[1115,1188,209,230]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.9" pageId="25" pageNumber="158" unit="mm" value="29.0">29 µm</quantity>
; head margin behind eyes with very few short setae which usually concentrate at the occipital corners, nCH 2.1, OccHL 
<quantity box="[1287,1359,273,294]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="25" pageNumber="158" unit="mm" value="30.0">30 µm</quantity>
